message.body: I just tried to take out Simone and both doors were locked. I will try again later to see if one of your roomies is around...
Oops...Patrick or ben should be home. Or if Nick comes for the lead test you could ask him. Ill have to copy my key.
Wanna text one of those guys to unlock the back door if they get a chance?
No luck. I will stop over there again in a bit.
Patrick took her out back so she should be OK till430. Thanks!
